documentation.text: Mappings that store our swap details.
On setup, we need to know the hashlock and participants.
Once Alice deposits her premium, we want to check that she deposited the correct amount.
Once Bob escrows his asset, we want to check that he escrowed the correct amount.
If the swap succeeds, Alice will collect her asset.
If the swap fails, Bob will redeem Alice's premium after the timout deadline.
If the swap fails, Bob can get his asset back after the timout deadline.
